briefdescription.para: Emitted when the widget's extent is changed.
Collapsible group box for configuration of extent, typically for a save operation.

detaileddescription.para: Besides allowing the user to enter the extent manually, it comes with options to use original extent or extent defined by the current view in map canvas.
When using the widget, make sure to call setOriginalExtent(), setCurrentExtent() and setOutputCrs() during initialization.
